                        </div>
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <span class="card-tag">Feature</span>
                            <h3 class="card-title">Cross-Chain Bridge</h3>
                            <p class="card-description">Bridge your assets across multiple blockchains while maintaining privacy. Fast, secure, and decentralized.</p>
                            <a href="https://app.salvium.io/bridge" class="card-link">Learn More</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="ecosystem-card">
                        <div class="relative w-full h-48 md:h-64 overflow-hidden">
                            <img src="./images/newimages/Blog Page/Blog Thumbs - No Text/Blog - No Text.jpg" alt="Yield Generation" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-50">
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <span class="card-tag">Feature</span>
                            <h3 class="card-title">Yield Generation</h3>
                            <p class="card-description">Generate passive income through our innovative yield farming strategies while maintaining complete privacy.</p>
                            <a href="https://app.salvium.io/yield" class="card-link">Learn More</a>
